{"tha-ap240:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap240:0.2":"Udakasanavagga ","tha-ap240:0.3":"Ambayagadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap240:1.1":"“Sake sippe apatthaddho, ","tha-ap240:1.2":"agamam kananam aham; ","tha-ap240:1.3":"Sambuddham yantam disvana, ","tha-ap240:1.4":"ambayagam adasaham. ","tha-ap240:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap240:2.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap240:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap240:2.4":"ambayagassidam phalam. ","tha-ap240:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap240:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap240:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap240:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ambayagadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap240:5.1":"Ambayagadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}